  "body": "- [ ] I've [opened a pull request ](https://github.com/trufflesuite/truffle/pull/4397) for this issue.\r\n\r\n---------------------------\r\n\r\n## Issue\r\n\r\nCalls type method code is calling getBlock() in the detect-network method which is not required. \r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\n`const instance = await MyContract.deployed();\r\nconst result = await instance.myMethod.call()`\r\n\r\nObserve network logs and you will find there is an extra getBlock method executed which is not required for calls type. \r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n\r\nCalls are free (do not need gas cost)\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\n\r\nPlease check network calls and you will see extra network calls for Calls type method. \r\n",
